      <title>德国总理肖尔茨不信任投票落败 为选举铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-chancellor-scholz-ask-parliament-clear-way-new-elections-2024-12-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国议会周一接受了德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨的邀请，撤回了对他和其政府的信任，为因朔尔茨政府垮台而不得不于 2 月 23 日提前举行选举扫清了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-chancellor-scholz-ask-parliament-clear-way-new-elections-2024-12-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:04:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将汇丰银行告上法庭，指控其忽视诈骗受害者</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/australian-regulator-sues-hsbc-australia-over-neglecting-scam-victims-2024-12-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚企业监管机构已对全球银行汇丰银行的当地分支机构提起法律诉讼，声称其未能正确回应约 950 起客户损失近一百万美元或更多的报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/australian-regulator-sues-hsbc-australia-over-neglecting-scam-victims-2024-12-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 21:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
